Package: visR
Type: Package
Title: A package to wrap functionality for plots, tables and diagrams adhering to graphical principles
Description: The goal of visR is to enable fit-for-purpose, reusable clinical and medcial research focused visualizations and tables with sensible defaults and based on sound graphical principles.
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2020-05-14
